text:
This project of yours has been going at least 11 years now? It feels a bit unreasonable to expect you to update as often as you did before, but I can't help but feel like these videos are like an anchor to my overall YouTube experience. This platform is unrecognisable from those days in 2007. Much has changed since then, furthermore most of my favourite youtubers from that era have moved on, but I've come to reliably expect SupraDarky to add new OSTs to his list.

It will be sad day when you inevitably have to finish your project, but it will be entirely understandable.
